# RA2YR ReSource — 全部限制统一在此
Checks: '-*,cppcoreguidelines-pro-bounds-pointer-arithmetic,cppcoreguidelines-pro-type-reinterpret-cast,cppcoreguidelines-pro-type-const-cast,cppcoreguidelines-pro-type-static-cast-downcast,cppcoreguidelines-slicing,bugprone-*,performance-*'
WarningsAsErrors: 'cppcoreguidelines-pro-bounds-pointer-arithmetic,cppcoreguidelines-pro-type-reinterpret-cast,cppcoreguidelines-pro-type-const-cast,cppcoreguidelines-pro-type-static-cast-downcast'
HeaderFilterRegex: '.*'
